Usage: setMaxCapPerFreq [-help] -cap {cap1 cap2 ...} [-force]
                        -freq {freq1 freq2 ...} [-lib <libName>]
                        -pins {cell pin}

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-cap {cap1 cap2 ...}        # specify a list of Nfreq capacitance values
                            # (list, required)
-force                      # Compute maxCap from interpolated -freq and -cap
                            # values (bool, optional)
-freq {freq1 freq2 ...}     # specify a list of at least two frequency values
                            # (list, required)
-lib <libName>              # specify library name (string, optional)
-pins {cell pin}            # Add new capacitance constraints to the specified
                            # set of cells and pins (list, required)